istry-is-threatening-teachers-to-return-to-work-on-the-gaza-border/0000018d-ac83-da6e-af9f-ac8b1f820000</link><description>尽管以色列告诉加沙边境的撤离人员可以留在酒店直到七月，但教育部不允许教师在其他学校担任职务，迫使他们回家或无薪离开</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 14:18:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/israels-education-ministry-is-threatening-teachers-to-return-to-work-on-the-gaza-border/0000018d-ac83-da6e-af9f-ac8b1f820000</guid></item><item><title>“这不是我们的第一次战争，但这是我们看到以色列信用评级下降的第一场战争”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-02-15/ty-article-podcast/this-is-not-our-first-war-but-its-the-first-war-weve-seen-israels-credit-rating-drop/0000018d-ac36-d221-af9f-efff2fb20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 14:09:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-02-15/ty-article-podcast/this-is-not-our-first-war-but-its-the-first-war-weve-seen-israels-credit-rating-drop/0000018d-ac36-d221-af9f-efff2fb20000</guid></item><item><title>“性是你首先要放弃的东西”：以色列人应对战争创伤、内疚和亲密关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/can-israelis-enjoy-sex-when-their-country-is-embroiled-in-war/0000018d-a7b1-da7e-a5ad-e7b37a9d0000</link><description>即使在战时，人们仍然继续发生性行为。但是，当你的儿子在加沙打仗或者你的父亲在那里成为人质时，你还能享受这样的生活吗？一群以色列性治疗师决定帮助以色列人回答这些问题</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 13:24:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/can-israelis-enjoy-sex-when-their-country-is-embroiled-in-war/0000018d-a7b1-da7e-a5ad-e7b37a9d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府奖励在该国北部、南部和约旦河西岸定居的新移民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-to-reward-new-immigrants-who-settle-in-countrys-periphery-and-west-bank/0000018d-ac36-da6e-af9f-ac3fffb70000</link><description>在法国、英国、美国和加拿大的犹太人对以色列移民兴趣日益浓厚的背景下，以色列计划向新“奥利姆”提供财政援助，以增加西方国家的移民</description><pub