rn-lebanon-kill-eleven-civilians-local-sources-say/0000018d-abca-da6e-af9f-abcbb0fc0000</guid></item><item><title>即使与埃及塞西冰释前嫌也无法让埃尔多安在加沙立足</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/even-burying-the-hatchet-with-egypts-sissi-cant-get-erdogan-a-foothold-in-gaza/0000018d-a975-d0cb-a5ef-bb7f43580000</link><description>开罗是卡塔尔的主要竞争对手，无意将土耳其纳入外交接触的核心圈，而且埃尔多安能否拿出任何成果值得怀疑。 ■ 与有能力发表对抗性言论的土耳其领导人不同，塞西承认，开罗和耶路撒冷之间合作关系的重要性</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 04:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/even-burying-the-hatchet-with-egypts-sissi-cant-get-erdogan-a-foothold-in-gaza/0000018d-a975-d0cb-a5ef-bb7f43580000</guid></item><item><title>以色列当局拆除东耶路撒冷社会活动家的住宅，引起美国愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-authorities-demolish-home-of-east-jerusalem-social-activist-drawing-u-s-ire/0000018d-a9ad-d0cb-a5ef-bbaf634c0000</link><description>美国国务院谴责耶路撒冷市政府的举动，称其“损害了促进可持续和平与安全的努力，以及以色列在世界上的地位”</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 04:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/israel-authorities-demolish-home-of-east-jerusalem-social-activist-drawing-u-s-ire/0000018d-a9ad-d0cb-a5ef-bbaf634c0000</guid></item><item><title>随着局势升级，真主党对以色列北部的伤害远不止火箭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-has-harmed-the-north-with-far-more-than-rockets-as-escalation-brews/0000018d-a91c-d0cb-a5ef-bb3e0cf20000</link><description>以色列军队和北部真主党之间的无情交火迫使以色列最北部社区的居民面临超现实的现实，其中许多人仍然流离失所。 “我们不知道从这里到哪里去。一名基布兹成员表示：“军队没有给我们答案”</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 04:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/hezbollah-has-harmed-the-north-with-far-more-than-rockets-as-escalation-brews/0000018d-a91c-d0cb-a5ef-bb3e0cf20000</guid></item><item><title>尼尔奥兹基布兹宣布人质亚伊尔·雅科夫（Yair Yaakov）死亡；士兵在加沙地带战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article-live/israeli-army-chief-were-focusing-on-being-prepared-for-war-in-the-north/0000018d-aac1-da6e-af9f-aac978980000</link><description>以色列军队辛贝特杀死了参与 10 月 7 日大屠杀的哈马斯指挥官，扣押了以色列人质 ■ 以色列国防部长对真主党表示：“我们在贝鲁特上空的飞机已经找到了目标” ■ 当地消息人士称，以色列在黎巴嫩的空袭造成 10 人死亡 ■ 美国报道称，阿拉伯国家预计将向巴勒斯坦国提交时间表 ■ 以色列国防军 24 小时内在约旦河西岸逮捕 22 名恐怖嫌疑人 ■ 世卫组织警告以色列对拉法的袭击将是一场“深不可测的灾难”</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 03:19:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article-live/israeli-army-chief-were-focusing-on-being-prepared-for-war-in-the-north/0000018d-aac1-da6e-af9f-aac978980000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质家属飞往海牙向哈马斯提出战争罪申诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-fly-to-the-hague-to-file-war-crime-complaint-against-hamas/0000018d-a932-d0cb-a5ef-bb3eef450000</link><description>在接下来的几周内，被释放的人质预计将在人质家属的私人倡议闭门听证会上作证，旨在在以色列不参与的情况下推进针对哈马斯的程序</description><pubDate>Thu, 15 Feb 2024 00:06:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/families-of-israeli-hostages-fly-to-the-hague-to-file-war-crime-complaint-against-hamas/0000018d-a932-d0cb-a5ef-bb3eef450000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦领导人阿巴斯在结束战争和继续掌权之间走钢丝</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-leader-abbas-walking-a-tightrope-between-ending-the-war-and-staying-in-power/0000018d-a976-da6e-af9f-a97f31ca0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦总统向哈马斯公开请求的时机引起了巴勒斯坦街头的不满，许多人将其与他受到卡塔尔的压力联系起来</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 23:53:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-15/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-leader-abbas-walking-a-tightrope-between-ending-the-war-and-staying-in-power/0000018d-a976-da6e-af9f-a97f31ca0000</guid></item><item><title>在即时阴谋时代，一个简单的拼写错误就会引发病毒般的仇恨</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-14/ty-article/.highlight/in-the-age-of-instant-conspiracies-a-simple-typo-is-fuel-for-viral-hate/0000018d-a981-d0cb-a5ef-bbaf3ba40000</link><description>唉，人为错误并不像另一个由于人们无法接受哈马斯令人发指的行为的现实而编造的不成比例的不切实际的寓言那么令人兴奋</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 21:47:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-14/ty-article/.highlight/in-the-age-of-instant-conspiracies-a-simple-typo-is-fuel-for-viral-hate/0000018d-a981-d0cb-a5ef-bbaf3ba40000</guid></item></channel></rss>